TL;DR;
- Database indexes are easy and powerful tools for performance enginering - An internal performance monitor enables quick insights into service performance  &nbsp;
Prologue: Two Research Projects Project #1 - In Zeeguu we research how we can make learning a foreign language more fun. We monitor a learners interactions with foreign texts and based on this we recommend further personalized reading and personalized vocabulary exercises.
The Zeeguu web application has a classical client-server architecture with the backend being implemnted with Flask &ndash; one of the most popular web application frameworks for Python.
